ss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Fdaily-property%2F3475253%2F&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=bb2133a230a5342f505ca0110514ce08&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.stheadline.com/daily-property/3475253/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;三年內萬元尺&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31988560&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1467915175687fbe357ec925_60683915"/><published>2025-07-23T00:10:06+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f420626a401636504f5b3fa57c2f360a</id><title>雞@心</title><updated>2025-07-21T00:51:41+08:00</updated><author><name>clamchowder</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-21T00:51:41+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573301972"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573301972"&gt;八號改三號，即刻出門搵飯食。好多地方無開，或者多人到無位。最後行遠啲，嚟呢間快餐。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;封面&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16379916" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="573301972" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250721/20250721_fd1d3d34086fb3744d9ePoZuCu4YQGYR.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/d8d278/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250721/20250721_fd1d3d34086fb3744d9ePoZuCu4YQGYR.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16379916_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16379916&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20250720_204849_HDR.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (89.97 KB)&